yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >开发环境：Eclipse+JDK1.7+Tomcat7+MySQL5.5+Nginx+Maven+SVN</span><span style=3D"font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >项目架构：Spring+SpringMVC+MyBatis+Redis+RabbitMQ+Quartz+Solr+jQuery+easyUI</span><span style=3D"font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >开发周期：7个月（未上线）</span><span style=3D"font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >项目描述：会购网上商城是一个综合性的B2C平台。会员可以在商城浏览商品、下订单，以及参加各种活动。会购网上商城采用分布式系统架构、RESTFUL风格接口，子系统之间通过调用服务使用http协议传递json数据。为了提高系统的性能使用Redis做系统缓存，并使用Redis实现session共享。为了保证Redis的可用性使用了Redis集群。</span><span style=3D"font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >主要模块有：后台管理系统，前台系统，登录系统，会员系统，订单系统，搜索系统。</span><span style=3D"font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:21.0000pt;" ><span style=3D"font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width=3D682  valign=3Dcenter  colspan=3D2  style=3D"width:511.5000pt;padding:0.0000pt 7.5000pt 0.0000pt 7.5000pt ;" ><table class=3DMsoNormalTable  style=3D"border-collapse:collapse;margin-left:10.8000pt;mso-padding-alt:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><tr><td width=3D83  valign=3Dtop  style=3D"width:62.3000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:21.0000pt;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >责任描述：</span><span style=3D"font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width=3D578  valign=3Dtop  style=3D"width:434.1500pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:21.0000pt;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >后台管理系统：富文本商品信息的CRUD，前台首页内容管理系统（CMS）；</span><span style=3D"font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >登录系统：利用Cookies存储Token，以Token为键将用户信息存储在Redis缓存中，并暴露接口用于其他系统查询验证用户信息；</span><span style=3D"font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >购物车系统：将商品添加购物车、查看购物车、修改购物车、提供商品选购存储和非即时操作的解决方案；</span><span style=3D"font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:21.0000pt;" ><span style=3D"font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:21.0000pt;" ><span style=3D"fo